column1: # This is sample csv file to generate ipc runs for the config. User can    #
# add new lines to generate respective test run command as per requirement.#
# Each test has different set of arguments and same are mentioned in the   #
# intermediate comments below.we can edit this file and run gen_spa_cmds.pl#
# script in config directory 'cfg_dir/scripts/gen_spa_cmds.pl'. Always run #
# it from config directory. Output file 'performance_runs' in config dir.  #
# gets updated after running the script to add new run commands to it      #
# Script runs in the build flow to dump a sample output file.              #
